# --- Deploy exception ---
# Streamlit Community Cloud's filesystem is ephemeral and there's no build
# step that can run the live-API pipeline (extract.py/credibility.py need
# GROQ_API_KEY + real time). So the finished Zomato database + its vector
# store are committed deliberately for the public demo, overriding the
# general *.db / chroma_db_*/ rules above. Keep these small and curated --
# do NOT un-ignore the raw zomato.csv or Yelp JSON dumps.
!truerating_zomato.db
!chroma_db_zomato/
!chroma_db_zomato/**